---
import ProductLayout from '../../layouts/ProductLayout.astro';

const title = "Bespoke Joinery Projects Carlisle, Cumbria | Woodstyle Joinery";
const description = "One-off bespoke joinery in Carlisle, Cumbria. Staircases, furniture, panelling, and custom commissions handcrafted to your design when nothing off-the-shelf will do.";

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What kind of bespoke projects do you take on?",
    answer: "All sorts, from staircases and fitted furniture to panelling, window seats, bars, and unusual one-off commissions. If it can be made from timber and joinery, it's worth asking us about."
  },
  {
    question: "I have an idea but no drawings. Can you still help?",
    answer: "Yes. Plenty of our bespoke work starts as a rough idea or a photo. We'll talk it through, take measurements, and work up a design with you before we build anything, so you know exactly what you're getting."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you match existing joinery or period features?",
    answer: "We can. We regularly match new work to existing staircases, mouldings, and panelling so a bespoke addition blends in with the original rather than standing out."
  },
  {
    question: "How do I get a quote for a bespoke project in Carlisle or Cumbria?",
    answer: "Call us on 01228 512303 or use our contact form and tell us what you have in mind. We will arrange to discuss it, then prepare a design and a free, no-obligation quote."
  }
];

const images = [
  { src: "/images/products/bespoke/IMG_7863.jpeg", alt: "Bespoke handcrafted joinery project in Carlisle, Cumbria", caption: "Bespoke Joinery Project" },
  { src: "/images/products/bespoke/IMG_7864.jpeg", alt: "Bespoke handcrafted joinery project in Carlisle, Cumbria", caption: "Custom Timber Commission" },
];
---

<ProductLayout {title} heading="Bespoke Projects" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>Some jobs don't fit neatly into a category, and those are often the ones we enjoy most. If you've got an idea for a piece of joinery and can't find anything off-the-shelf that does it, this is where we come in.</p>

    <p>Over the years we've built staircases, fitted furniture, panelling, window seats, bars, media units, and all manner of one-off commissions. Whatever it is, we'll sit down with you, work up a design, and make it properly from solid timber.</p>

    <p>If you can picture it, there's a good chance we can build it. Give us a call on <strong>01228 512303</strong> and tell us what you've got in mind.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Bespoke staircases, balustrades, and handrails</li>
      <li>Fitted and freestanding furniture built to your design</li>
      <li>Panelling, window seats, and feature joinery</li>
      <li>One-off commissions when nothing standard will do</li>
      <li>Designed with you and handcrafted from solid timber</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>
